# 📝 To-Do List Application

A simple command-line To-Do List application built using Python. This project allows users to add, view, and delete tasks through a menu-driven interface.

## 🚀 Features

- Add new tasks
- View all tasks
- Delete existing tasks
- Exit the application
- Handles invalid task deletion gracefully

## 📌 Concepts Used

- Python Lists
- Loops (`while`)
- Conditional Statements (`if-elif-else`)
- User Input
- List Methods (`append`, `remove`)
- Menu-Driven Programming


